OL,3,C'Doting and caring niece' jailed for
OL,4,Cconning her 84-year-old uncle out of
OL,5,C#200k
OL,7,FA woman who was supposed to be caring
OL,8,Ffor her elderly uncle "concocted a web
OL,9,Fof lies" to steal more than #200,000.
OL,11,FPamela Urvoy used the money to buy a
OL,12,Fhouse in Blackburn which she promised
OL,13,Fwould be in both of their names, but
OL,14,Fin reality only belonged to her.
OL,16,FPreston Crown Court heard that in 2008
OL,17,FUrvoy's uncle suffered a serious
OL,18,Fstroke which left him unable to live
OL,19,Fan independent life. Shortly after his
OL,20,Fstroke, Urvoy moved into his home in
OL,21,FPadiham, Burnley, to act as his carer.
