OL,7,FIn 2013, a new property was purchased
OL,8,Fin Garsden Avenue in Blackburn for
OL,9,F#230,000 and the victim believed this
OL,10,Fwas a joint venture between himself
OL,11,Fand Urvoy and ownership of the house
OL,12,Fwas split between them.
OL,14,FBut after Urvoy's uncle was
OL,15,Ftemporarily placed in a care home,
OL,16,Fsocial services became concerned about
OL,17,Fwho was looking after his finances and
OL,18,Flaunched an investigation.
