OL,7,FChecks with Land Registry showed that
OL,8,Fthe property in Garsden Avenue was
OL,9,Fsolely in Urvoy's name.
OL,11,FShe initially claimed that the
OL,12,Fmajority of the money for the purchase
OL,13,F` #203,000 - had come from an
OL,14,Finheritance, but when asked for proof,
OL,15,FUrvoy later claimed her uncle had
OL,16,Fgifted her the money.
OL,18,FThe court also heard the victim was
OL,19,Fsleeping in a cellar basement room,
OL,20,Fill cared for which caused serious
OL,21,Fconcerns to social services.
