OL,3,C'Doting and caring niece' jailed for
OL,4,Cconning her 84-year-old uncle out of
OL,5,C#200k
OL,7,FUrvoy, of Garsden Avenue, Blackburn,
OL,8,Fwas charged with two counts of fraud
OL,9,Fby false representation. The first
OL,10,Frelating to her uncle and the second
OL,11,Frelating to the claim she made to the
OL,12,Fconveyance that she was the sole
OL,13,Fpurchaser of the property.
OL,15,FUrvoy was jailed on Friday 14 November
OL,16,Ffor four years, but her uncle did not
OL,17,Flive to see justice as he died in
OL,18,FMarch 2024.
