OL,7,F"Having worked to ensure his later
OL,8,Fyears in life would be comfortable
OL,9,Ffinancially, it must have come as a
OL,10,Fgreat shock to find out that all of
OL,11,Fhis money had gone. And the person
OL,12,Fresponsible for doing that was a
OL,13,Ffamily member.
OL,15,F"Despite the evidential difficulties
OL,16,Fof the victim having died, the passage
OL,17,Fof time we will endeavour to seek
